245
00:20:54,755 --> 00:20:55,475
Hein?

246
00:20:55,475 --> 00:20:57,175
"Sai Baba".

247
00:20:57,175 --> 00:21:00,235
Ce Shirdi Sai Nath?

248
00:21:00,235 --> 00:21:02,495
Le faux Sai Baba.

249
00:21:02,495 --> 00:21:03,915
C'est un autre gars?

250
00:21:04,095 --> 00:21:04,775
Oui

251
00:21:12,515 --> 00:21:19,375
